{"tid":1410413,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"突發 屯門消防局有速龍","createTime":"2019-08-05T01:30:59.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-05T01:40:53.000Z","uid":238040,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"d333ea25c3d809e6de0fba56bd3c0102a1f28138","tid":1410413,"uid":238040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T01:30:59.000Z","msg":"我地關注組收到一個已fact check 消息<br />\n聽日8月5嘅集會<br />\n屯門消防局會有速龍小隊standby<br />\n<br />\n我地關注組望過地圖，地理上，如果有手足去圍狗屋，畜龍從消防局後門出就可以包抄<br />\n<br />\n同埋，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">好大可能其他6區嘅消防局都會係咁部署</span>。所以，去集會嘅手足要有所提防<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nPvG8wU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnPvG8wU.jpg&h=dd56e00a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">Full gear打狗#，未撚驚過</span></span>"},{"pid":"860fe5a164ffa16210d639da51c8a3ef4c20e5fc","tid":1410413,"uid":2220,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T01:33:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UStNjFG.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUStNjFG.png&h=d4acef2b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"471a1b48fe87587133e7c6b50d3e919ed1b87961","tid":1410413,"uid":63666,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"860fe5a164ffa16210d639da51c8a3ef4c20e5fc","tid":1410413,"uid":2220,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T01:33:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UStNjFG.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUStNjFG.png&h=d4acef2b&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T01:36:07.000Z","msg":"係屯門警署呀 響西鐵站隔離<br />\n青山警署2邊都係住宅 幾入下"},{"pid":"0962237a08169c812761f3248ad8a37aeb90029f","tid":1410413,"uid":275634,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T01:36:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\